## Workshop demo-seed

`integration-layer/database/seeds/demo-workshop.mjs` seeder idempotent demodata (6 brukere, 3 flerbygg-runder, 10 MDU-deals over hele pipelinen + begge war-room-utfall, 7 cases, 5 DB-backede bonuser). Kjør fra `integration-layer/` med `DATABASE_PUBLIC_URL` satt — ikke `railway run` lokalt (intern host resolver ikke).

